# HTML Hello World Project

## How to Run

1. Download and unzip the project folder.
2. Open the folder in File Explorer.
3. Double-click **index.html**.
4. The page opens in your default browser — no server needed.

> **Tip:** For a better experience, right-click `index.html` → *Open with* → choose Chrome, Edge, or Firefox.

---

## What You Will See

A centred card on a light background with the text **"Hello, World! 👋"**.

